body:
for david berman, who died yesterday (

[https://pitchfork.com/news/david-berman-silver-jews-purple-mountains-dead-at-52/](https://pitchfork.com/news/david-berman-silver-jews-purple-mountains-dead-at-52/)

) and whose music and poetry have brought me so much happiness.

for my favorite silver jews album, _american water_ (\_\_\_PARAGRAPH\_BREAK\_\_\_

[https://open.spotify.com/album/7LO24Uu9c0vuFUtHDAj0Wa?si=PBc\_ranNTy2ECjthuEvO3Q&nd=1](https://open.spotify.com/album/7LO24Uu9c0vuFUtHDAj0Wa?si=PBc_ranNTy2ECjthuEvO3Q&nd=1)

), and for the great new purple mountains album (\_\_\_PARAGRAPH\_BREAK\_\_\_

[https://open.spotify.com/album/5NCdiiTgky5PbjmCtcgwtn?si=ookjV9dpT16Jw9tsW\_9aDQ&nd=1](https://open.spotify.com/album/5NCdiiTgky5PbjmCtcgwtn?si=ookjV9dpT16Jw9tsW_9aDQ&nd=1)) which was such a wonderful surprise.

this recording i made in a past life of his perfect summer poem called "the charm of 5:30" and the silver jews song "honk if you're lonely": 

[https://firmuhment-blog.tumblr.com/post/5833917416](https://firmuhment-blog.tumblr.com/post/5833917416)

